"A.P.238/4/7": "The event right? I heard about it on the monitor. But I'm really not interested."
"The only thing I'm interested in, is how to get stronger to get rid of more Darkers."
"If I had the power to be able to get rid of Dark Falz then..."
"... she wouldn't have had to die."
"Why? Why did it have to be her that died?"
"Why? She didn't have all of that much talent, but she tried her best every single day..."
"And just when she thought she had finally realized her dream..."
"All I can do is get rid of all of the Darkers with out thinking about it."
"I think that's the only thing that I can do."
"I'm going to get going. At the event I'll try to get rid of as many as possible."
